					<_h3>Your desktop is even smarter!</_h3>
					<_p>OpenMandriva Lx makes you all free to configure your environment for your needs. 
					Personalizable, modular, scalable, efficient and full of visual effects if you so wish: 
					take your pick. As an exclusivity, discover all functionalities of smart desktop. 
					Define your environment based on the use you put it to. Label your documents, your images, 
					your emails, identify your projects. .</_p>
				</li>
				<li><img src="style/images/img2.png" alt="Needs" />
					<_h3>Your desktop fits your needs.</_h3>
					<_p>Switch your desktop into a multimedia center or a light netbook environment: it's as easy as a click.
					You have full access to thousands of softwares: multimedia, office system, graphics, Internet, development...
					Improve your desktop experience and get more than an Operating System!.</_p>
				</li>
				<li><img src="style/images/img3.png" alt="Easy" />
					
					<_h3>Your desktop is simple and secure.</_h3>
					<_p>Easy-to-use goes hand in hand with the security of your data and your family. OpenMandriva Lx comes with
					a full set of powerful administration tools. Printer configuration, network and mobility management,
					but also personal firewall, network and applications access control for children... Your environment is free,
					easy and all secure!</_p>
				</li>
			</ul>
